Detailed Description

The response contains a list of tunnel protocols supported by the device. See ZSE Profile Spec. r17, Figure D.47.

Field Documentation

uint8_t _ZclSupportedTunnelProtocolsResponsePayload_t::protocolListComplete
  • A value of 0 indicates that there are more supported protocols available (if more than 16 protocols are supported).
  • A value of 1 indicates that the list of supported protocols is complete.
